{"tid":1404584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[85罷工] 星期一搭地鐵不如帶D糖同零食，派俾受影響乘客食，同埋塞住廢中廢老把臭口？","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:50:08.000Z","uid":76632,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"50da1b674cb12535bc6c8720e5baa8f019902dc5","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">戴定頭盔，地鐵禁止飲食。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n困車期間，總係有藍絲師奶廢老(通常都貪小便宜)係到嘈嘈閉，不如派D低級零食俾佢地，塞住個木嘴，然後再同地鐵職員講佢地係車廂飲食罰藍絲錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，其他乘客通常都未食早餐，不如派D中級零食俾佢地表示友好，以爭取更多市民支持不合作運動？"},{"pid":"7e8dd5b95aa55e56c1afa12bb1b191a062100b06","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"只推5次，第1次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b27b067c396598902d0a6517e20ab3e0af6f5c1","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"推第2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeda0df2972807813c2cee85f766df4e7f8fcde4","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"推第3次"},{"pid":"5f0fb2fd930b5fae9b3139a180c3e79f60f3b875","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"推第4次"},{"pid":"6b8d1d6bed6e43e395b515959a45e58ee682741d","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"last push"},{"pid":"7454eef2ea1a8886ebdaa3a19615c81edc95f8b8","tid":1404584,"uid":54876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"派紙巾啦，老野點食糖"},{"pid":"d5d6e68e7e44e022fd8de3012db52bb620b25e17","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7454eef2ea1a8886ebdaa3a19615c81edc95f8b8","tid":1404584,"uid":54876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"派紙巾啦，老野點食糖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"藍絲廢老好鍾意妹下妹下，想用硬糖塞住佢把臭口。<br />\n<br />\n自己友就派零食薯片之類。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">戴多次頭盔，車廂不准飲食</span>"},{"pid":"5f076d2311834eb19c38ca2589a46212993cb849","tid":1404584,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"香蕉軟糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc09b9e1406e6b19e4f4eb9f4c2067bf0670b64","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5f076d2311834eb19c38ca2589a46212993cb849","tid":1404584,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"香蕉軟糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zt50xZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzt50xZM.jpg&h=033118a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你地鍾意食軟糖嘅，我陣間就去買，又或者去夾糖鋪夾一大包派街坊。"},{"pid":"63efbeb8a6100da33b5a76b30ac646d0058a9805","tid":1404584,"uid":214482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3dc09b9e1406e6b19e4f4eb9f4c2067bf0670b64","tid":1404584,"uid":76632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5f076d2311834eb19c38ca2589a46212993cb849","tid":1404584,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"香蕉軟糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zt50x